    },
    {
      "id": "l0003",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "咳咳……",
      "note": "虚弱，咳嗽",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0004",
      "character_id": "xiaoguang",
      "text": "呼……这些扫地机器人上不来。",
      "note": "长舒一口气，带有劫后余生的得意",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0005",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "有本事你上来啊！",
      "note": "转身对着下方，挑衅地拍打屁股",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0006",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "我要坚持不住了！",
      "note": "满头大汗，绝望地挥舞手臂",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0007",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "小品！",
      "note": "惊恐尖叫",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0008",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "吸尘器和榨汁机背后都连着电线……只要把电闸关掉，断掉它们的电，就能让它们停下来。",
      "note": "恍然大悟，嘴角上扬",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0009",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "我们快去追黑桃5！",
      "note": "急促，指着前方",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0010",
      "character_id": "xiaoguang",
      "text": "别怕！区区几个手机怎么伤害得了我？",
      "note": "张开双臂，护在两人身前，不屑地冷笑",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0011",
      "character_id": "xiaoguang",
      "text": "怎么爆炸了……",
      "note": "声音虚弱，充满困惑",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0012",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "还不赶紧跑！",
      "note": "大惊失色，转身就跑",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0013",
      "character_id": "heibang-zhangguan",
      "text": "小品他们就这样肆无忌惮地在大街上搞破坏，你们是怎么做事的？！立即出动，抓捕小品！",
      "note": "暴跳如雷，厉声训斥",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0014",
      "character_id": "jixie-tejingmen",
      "text": "是！",
      "note": "机械、整齐划一的声音",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0015",
      "character_id": "tejing-duizhang",
      "text": "这些活过来的电器是怎么回事？！",
      "note": "惊恐，结巴",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0016",
      "character_id": "jixie-tejingmen",
      "text": "救命啊！",
      "note": "四下逃窜，发出凄惨的叫声",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0017",
      "character_id": "tongxunyuan",
      "text": "小品，扑克牌组织的黑桃5，他擅长使用纳米机器人。这些机器人可以暂时使智能电器动起来，并且听他的指令做事。",
      "note": "语速极快，专业且急迫",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0018",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "它们怎么接收指令的？",
      "note": "推了推眼镜，眉头紧锁",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0019",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "这些电器上都带有Wi-Fi标志，难道是通过Wi-Fi信号？",
      "note": "眼神一亮，指着电器的外壳",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0020",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "果然！破坏掉Wi-Fi信号接收器，就能切断纳米机器人和黑桃5之间的联系。通讯员，帮我屏蔽这片区域的Wi-Fi信号。",
      "note": "得意地插着腰，对着手表说",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0021",
      "character_id": "tongxunyuan",
      "text": "没问题。",
      "note": "自信地敲击虚拟键盘",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0022",
      "character_id": "heitao5",
      "text": "可笑。断网又怎么样？我的纳米机器人还可以连接卫星网络。",
      "note": "冷笑一声，语气充满不屑",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0023",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "没有用！这些电器又开始攻击了！",
      "note": "大惊失色，举起拖把防御",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0024",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "怎么回事？通讯员？断网联系不上她了！",
      "note": "焦急地拍打手表",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0025",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "原来这些纳米机器人，它们是根据人脸数据进行识别攻击。而我的脸型比较特殊，系统根本没有办法分清是脸还是馒头……",
      "note": "站起身，摸着下巴，恍然大悟",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0026",
      "character_id": "yanjing",
      "text": "那我有办法了！我用3D打印出小品的脸面具，所有人戴上，就能迷惑纳米机器人系统！",
      "note": "兴奋地打了个响指，从背包掏出一个便携设备",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0027",
      "character_id": "xiaoguang",
      "text": "还得是小品的馒头脸有用！",
      "note": "双手合十，满眼星星，崇拜地看着小品",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0028",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "胡说，明明靠的是我的帅脸！",
      "note": "单手插兜，撩了一下头发，自信地撇嘴",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0029",
      "character_id": "tongxunyuan",
      "text": "小品，我入侵了卫星网络系统，终于联系上你了。我已经查到黑桃5带着红心4去了一个地下诊所，我马上把地址发给你。",
      "note": "神情严肃，操作着虚拟面板",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
      "temporary_binding": null
    },
    {
      "id": "l0030",
      "character_id": "xiaopin",
      "text": "收到。我们马上过去！",
      "note": "眼神变得锐利，握紧拳头",
      "language": "zh",
      "engine_override": null,
      "profile_override": null,
      "binding_override": null,
      "service_override": null,
